\par <#/>}{\b\fs24\lang2057 THE Attorney-General, Mr Amos Wako, yesterday lifted the ban imposed by his predecessor, Mr Justice Matthew Guy Muli, on the }{\b\i\fs24\lang2057 Nairobi Law Monthly}{\b\fs24\lang2057  magazine.
