\par <#/>On banning the magazine last October, Mr Justice Muli said in a legal notice 420, 1990: "In exercise of po
wers conferred to me by section 52 of the Penal Code, the AG makes the following order: the prohibited publications Order 1990. <#/>All past, present and future issues of the periodical publication entitled }{\i\fs24\lang2057 Nairobi Law Monthly}{
