 in Yatta location when they accidentally fell into it and drowned. <#/>Their bodies are at the city mortuary for a post-mortem examination.
\par <#/>Pius Ombewa Ogimbo, in an attempt to cross a swollen Nyakwere River, Ahero, Kisumu, for Sangorota Market, slipped into it and drowned.
