on got into the country. <#/>"Must a parent be killed on account of the activities of the <-/offsprings>?" she wondered. <#/>She said she told the officers that Koigi was knowledgeable and mature enough to do things on his own without parental supervision
 or permission. <#/>"You are the law, you have the long arm to get him and you can do with him what you will," was her reply to some questions posed by the officers.
